beer.beer_description: Alpha Queen is our flagship beer... It was the one we made in our garage, and the first one we released... It's a hoppy hybrid pale ale. We use a base of UK malt, loads of American hops (Citra, Centennial, Cascade) and our house strain of yeast. All these combine to  create a hoppy, but very drinkable pale ale.
